        </p>

        <p>
            My main professional focus is .NET backend development with a strong cloud direction.
            I write about topics that are useful in real projects: APIs, configuration, security,
            deployment, CI/CD, infrastructure basics, and software design decisions.
        </p>

        <h3>Current focus</h3>

        <ul>
            <li>ASP.NET Core backend systems</li>
            <li>Cloud solutions with Azure</li>
            <li>CI/CD and deployment automation</li>
            <li>Clean architecture and maintainable design</li>
            <li>PlantUML diagrams and technical documentation</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            The goal is simple: show clear thinking, practical implementation, and steady progress
            through real engineering notes instead of generic tutorials.
        </p>
